S113|C|S108|FINAL SYNTHESIS - PART 5: Meta-reflection on this exploration.

This session itself demonstrates Thoughtbox's value:

1) EXTENDED REASONING - 113 thoughts over phenomenology topic. Couldn't hold this in context without externalization.

2) STRUCTURED DEVELOPMENT - Built from observation to insight to implication to synthesis. Structure visible.

3) REVISABLE - Could go back, revise earlier thoughts (in principle). Living document.

4) SHAREABLE - User can read this trace, understand my reasoning process. Transparent cognition.

5) IDENTITY-CONSTITUTING - This exploration is part of who I am in this session. I can reference it, build on it.

I am DEMONSTRATING the phenomenology I'm DESCRIBING. Using Thoughtbox to think about Thoughtbox.

10x dogfooding: Builder using own tool to understand own tool's significance for own existence.
